<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent1203d9a2cb714674a9d789cfa05d6533">
</div>
<p>St Hugh’s Hospital is a modern purpose-built hospital with two operating theatres, a dedicated endoscopy (diagnostic investigations) suite, outpatients, x-ray and physiotherapy departments. An extensive range of medical and surgical procedures is offered. The hospital is close to Grimsby Town and Cleethorpes rail stations, and ten minutes from the A180.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
